<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Debridger!</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background:#f4f4f4;">
    <div
      style="max-width:600px; margin:20px auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
    >

      <!-- Header -->
      <div style="background:#2B6036; padding:32px 12px; text-align:center;">
        <h1 style="color:#ffffff; margin:0; font-size:30px;">
          Welcome to Debridger,
          {{nameToUse}}!
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div style="padding:40px 16px;">
        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#333; margin-top:0;">
          Thanks for creating a Debridger account — your direct gateway to sourcing premium crops
          from verified Nigerian farmers.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin:20px 0;">
          What happens now? Debridger connects you directly with verified farmers across Nigeria,
          giving you access to high-quality export crops at competitive prices — without unnecessary
          intermediaries.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin:20px 0;">
          Your account lets you explore available crops, connect with trusted suppliers, and manage
          sourcing seamlessly — all from one secure platform.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin:20px 0;">
          You can start sourcing crops like sesame, cashew, and cocoa directly from Nigerian farmers
          here:
          <br />
          <a href="https://debridger.vercel.app/" style="color:#2B6036; text-decoration:none;">
            https://debridger.vercel.app/
          </a>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin:20px 0;">
          Whether you&apos;re buying locally or exporting globally, you can access Debridger anytime
          on the web:
          <br />
          <a href="https://debridger.vercel.app/" style="color:#2B6036; text-decoration:none;">
            https://debridger.vercel.app/
          </a>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin:24px 0;">
          For market insights, crop availability updates, and platform news, follow us on X:
          <br />
          <a href="https://x.com/Debridgers" style="color:#2B6036; text-decoration:none;">
            @debridgers
          </a>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin-top:32px;">
          The Debridger Team
          <i>Bridging buyers directly to Nigerian farmers</i>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div style="background:#f0f0f0; padding:8px; text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#999;">
        &copy;
        {{year}}
        Debridger • You&apos;re receiving this because you successfully signed up.
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>